{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Legislation", "legislationType": "StateAdministrativeRule", "legislationJurisdiction": "US-VT", "name": "Vermont - Vermont Administrative Rules (Agentic Discovery) - A1", "identifier": "VT-AGENTIC-A1", "description": "Vermont - Wikipedia", "text": "Vermont - Wikipedia\nJump to content\nMain menu\nMain menu\nmove to sidebar\nhide\nNavigation\nMain page\nContents\nCurrent events\nRandom article\nAbout Wikipedia\nContact us\nContribute\nHelp\nLearn to edit\nCommunity portal\nRecent changes\nUpload file\nSpecial pages\nSearch\nSearch\nAppearance\nDonate\nCreate account\nLog in\nPersonal tools\nDonate\nCreate account\nLog in\nContents\nmove to sidebar\nhide\n(Top)\n1\nToponymy\n2\nHistory\nToggle History subsection\n2.1\nPre-colonial\n2.2\nColonial\n2.3\nSovereignty\n2.4\nRevolutionary War\n2.5\nAdmission to the Union\n2.6\nCivil War\n2.7\nPost–Civil War to the present\n2.7.1\nDemographic changes\n2.7.2\nPolitical changes\n3\nGeography\nToggle Geography subsection\n3.1\nCities\n3.2\nLargest towns\n3.3\nClimate\n3.3.1\nClimate change\n3.4\nGeology\n3.5\nFauna\n3.6\nFlora\n4\nDemographics\nToggle Demographics subsection\n4.1\nPopulation\n4.1.1\nRace and ethnicity\n4.1.2\nVital statistics\n4.2\nDialect\n4.3\nReligion\n5\nEconomy\nToggle Economy subsection\n5.1\nPersonal income\n5.2\nAgriculture\n5.2.1\nDairy farming\n5.2.2\nForestry\n5.2.3\nOther\n5.3\nManufacturing\n5.4\nEnergy\n5.5\nHealth\n5.6\nLabor\n5.7\nInsurance\n5.8\nRecreation\n5.8.1\nHunting\n5.8.2\nSkiing and snowmobiling\n5.9\nQuarrying\n5.10\nNonprofits and volunteerism\n6\nEducation\nToggle Education subsection\n6.1\nHigher education\n7\nTransportation\nToggle Transportation subsection\n7.1\nRoad\n7.1.1\nMajor north–south routes\n7.1.2\nMajor east–west routes\n7.2\nFerry\n7.3\nRail\n7.4\nIntercity bus\n7.5\nLocal bus\n7.6\nAir\n8\nMedia\nToggle Media subsection\n8.1\nNewspapers of record\n8.2\nBroadcast and web media\n9\nElectrical utilities\n10\nPublic health\n11\n